fields.name: Silver C48 Road Bike
fields.description: Experience smooth, high-speed rides with this lightweight silver road bike, designed for performance and endurance. Featuring an aerodynamic aluminum frame, precision Shimano gearing, and responsive disc brakes, this bike offers the perfect balance of speed, control, and comfort. Ideal for both casual riders and serious cyclists, its sleek silver finish adds a touch of elegance to every ride.

fields.name: Ribble CDR Road Bike
fields.description: Designed for performance and visibility, the Ribble Illuminous Yellow Road Bike combines a lightweight aerodynamic frame, precision Shimano gearing, and responsive disc brakes for ultimate control. Its bold high-visibility yellow finish ensures you stand out on the road, day or night. Whether you're training, commuting, or racing, this bike delivers speed, comfort, and style in one sleek package.

fields.name: Focus White Road Bike
fields.description: The Felt White Road Bike is built for cyclists who demand speed, precision, and a sleek design. Featuring a lightweight aerodynamic frame, smooth Shimano gearing, and responsive disc brakes, it delivers exceptional performance on any road. The crisp white finish adds a touch of elegance, making it the perfect blend of style and speed. Whether you're training or commuting, this bike ensures a smooth and efficient ride.

fields.name: Trek SLX Blue Road Bike
fields.description: Designed for speed and endurance, the Trek Blue Road Bike features a lightweight aerodynamic frame for effortless performance on the road. Its smooth-shifting drivetrain ensures seamless gear changes, while powerful disc brakes provide reliable stopping power in all conditions. With a striking blue finish, this bike offers both style and high performance, making it the perfect choice for cyclists who crave adventure.

fields.name: BH Red Road Bike
fields.description: Built for performance, the BH Red Road Bike combines a lightweight, aerodynamic frame with a responsive drivetrain for smooth, efficient rides. Its bold red finish exudes speed and style, while reliable braking and agile handling ensure confidence on any terrain. Whether you're racing, training, or tackling long-distance rides, this bike is designed to keep you moving fast and in control.

fields.name: Polygon White Mountain Bike
fields.description: Conquer any trail with the Polygon White Mountain Bike, designed for durability, control, and versatility. Its lightweight yet sturdy frame, responsive suspension, and rugged all-terrain tires ensure a smooth ride over rough terrain. The crisp white finish adds a sleek, modern look, making it perfect for both trail enthusiasts and off-road adventurers. Get ready to ride with confidence and style!

fields.name: Norco Orange Mountain Bike
fields.description: Take on any trail with the Norco Orange Mountain Bike, engineered for strength, control, and all-terrain performance. Featuring a durable frame, responsive suspension, and grippy tires, this bike delivers smooth handling on rough terrain. Its bold orange finish ensures you stand out on the trails while riding with confidence and style. Ready for your next off-road adventure?

fields.name: T-129 Grey Mountain Bike
fields.description: The T-129 Grey Mountain Bike is built for riders who demand agility, control, and durability on rugged terrain. Its lightweight yet tough frame, advanced suspension system, and high-traction tires ensure a smooth and confident ride over any obstacle. With a sleek grey finish, this bike blends modern style with high-performance engineering, making it the perfect choice for trail enthusiasts and off-road adventurers.

fields.name: KU Orange Kids Bike
fields.description: The KU Orange Kids Bike is designed for young riders who love to explore! With a lightweight frame, easy-to-use brakes, and stable tires, it ensures a smooth and safe ride on any adventure. The bright orange finish adds a fun, energetic touch, making every ride exciting. Perfect for building confidence and enjoying the outdoors!

fields.name: Lumi Pink Kids Bike
fields.description: The Lumi Pink Kids Bike is perfect for little riders who love adventure! With a lightweight frame, easy-to-use brakes, and stable tires, it offers a smooth, safe, and comfortable ride. The vibrant pink design adds a touch of fun and style, making every ride exciting. Ideal for kids learning to ride and building confidence on two wheels!

fields.name: Kross Blue Balance Bike
fields.description: The Kross Blue Balance Bike is designed to help little riders develop balance and coordination with ease. Its lightweight frame, grippy tires, and comfortable handlebars provide a smooth and stable ride, making it the ideal first bike. The vibrant blue finish adds a fun and stylish touch, perfect for kids learning to ride with confidence!
